comments.en: An ontology for describing machine learning datasets, tasks, pipelines, experiments, software and publications. The ontology extends ML-Schema, DCAT, FaBiO and SDO.

abstract.value: An ontology for describing machine learning datasets, tasks, pipelines, experiments, software and publications. The ontology extends ML-Schema, DCAT, FaBiO and SDO.
